<!-- Service introduction section -->
<div id="div2">
<p> <img src="img1.png" width="100" height="100" style="vertical-align:middle">
    This website provides a service to transform a <em><b>long</b></em> URL(Uniform Resource Locator) to a <em><b>short</b></em> alias.
</p>
    <!-- User case introduction -->
    <h2>You CAN:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Enters a long URL for shortening
        </li>
        <li>Customizes your short URL
        </li>
        <li>Redirects the short URL to original long URL
        </li>
        <li>Keeps track of click data of a short URL
        </li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Instructions:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>First you should write the original URL in the "Input URL" textbox.
        </li>
        <li>By clicking <b><em>"Transform"</em></b> button, you will get a shortened URL generated by our service and
            shown in the "Output URL" textbox.</li>
        <li>You can also customize your own shortened URL. By writing your customized URL in the "Output URL" text box
            and clicking the <b><em>"Customize!"</em></b> button, your customized URL is confirmed if it hasn't been used.
        <li>You can only type in letters, numbers and dashes for your customized URL. </li>
    </ul>
</div>

